AGI - Killed and then the house burned. The fact happened in Montepiano>, a hamlet of the municipality of Vernio (Prato), where a woman was found dead inside a house burned down, a cottage near Lake Fiorenzo. The carabinieri,&nbsp; co-ordinated by prosecutor Tescaroli,&nbsp; investigate for murder.
According to a first reconstruction, the woman could have been killed in a knife and then the flames would have been attached to the house. Suspects focus on the victim's son, a 22-year-old boy. On the spot also sanitary of the 118 and the municipal police. The investigations are coordinated by the prosecutor of Prato Luca Tescaroli.&nbsp;
It is not clear yet the motive of the crime. According to the first information, the son would infer three pounded to his mother. The young, deaf, was found on the spot. Looks like the young man lived with his mother in the house.

